window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I now have my own clan, made up of five shifters and one mage. If we’re going to grow stronger, I’ll need to start making fat stacks of cash...by hunting monsters. </b></p> <p>Dragons are at the top of the supernatural food chain, so that should be a cinch. One thing that’s going to cause trouble though, is the return of the Nightlords. And then there’s the disappearance of the beautiful thunderbird shifter. I have a feeling that they’re somehow related, but it’s just a hunch.</p> <p>Either way, my Dragon’s Hoard is going to get rich, figure out what’s going on with the Nightlords, and save the thunderbird shifter.</p>"; 
